title: #569 - Kelvin Gastelum
description:
Kelvin Gastelum, an MMA fighter who is currently ranked #5 in the UFC's Middleweight division and the winner of The Ultimate Fighter 17, joins Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt LIVE in studio.
